    "status" : "extensions",
    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>http://va.gov/terminology/vistaDefinedElements/9000011-.12</code><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFproblemStatus.html\">VF_problemStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>A</td><td>ACTIVE</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-clinical.html#condition-clinical-active\">active</a></td></tr><tr><td>I</td><td>INACTIVE</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-clinical.html#condition-clinical-inactive\">inactive</a></td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-clinical.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/condition-clinical</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFproblemStatus.html\">VF_problemStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-clinical.html#condition-clinical-active\">active</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Active</td><td>The subject is currently experiencing the condition or situation, there is evidence of the condition or situation, or considered to be a significant risk.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-clinical.html#condition-clinical-inactive\">inactive</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Inactive</td><td>The subject is no longer experiencing the condition or situation and there is no longer evidence or appreciable risk of the condition or situation.</td><td/></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
